      "description": "Hi everyone! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and I think you\u2019re going to love it! It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really wonderful shape. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road for many more adventures. It drives smoothly, looks fantastic, and is just waiting for someone to take the wheel. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and see it in person\u2014I\u2019d love to show it to you!",
