    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its high-revving nature and individual throttle bodies. The powertrain delivers linear torque across the rev range, coupled with a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical mechanical maintenance has been prioritized, including addressed VANOS solenoids and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension has been enhanced with Bilstein dampers for superior compression and rebound characteristics. While the exterior shows minor aesthetic patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals\u2014including recent valve clearances and rod bearing inspections\u2014are in excellent health, making this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
